OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1775207142
OL,3,CFamily of electrocuted runner say not
OL,4,Cenough being done to similar future
OL,5,Cdeaths
OL,7,FThe family of a runner who died after
OL,8,Fbeing electrocuted by a low-hanging
OL,9,Felectricity cable says the response
OL,10,Ffrom the industry body, Energy Network
OL,11,FAssociation is "insulting".
OL,13,FJohn Henry Oates, known as Harry, was
OL,14,Ffound dead on 27 October 2023 in
OL,15,FLupton, near Kendal, while visiting
OL,16,Fhis parents. An inquest concluded that
OL,17,Fhe "died due to a rare and complex
OL,18,Fsequence of events".
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/11
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,354,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1775207142
OL,3,CFamily of electrocuted runner say not
OL,4,Cenough being done to similar future
OL,5,Cdeaths
OL,7,FCockermouth Coroner's Court heard the
OL,8,F29-year-old was training for a half-
OL,9,Fmarathon when he ran into the 11kv
OL,10,Felectricity line.
OL,12,FThe court heard how simultaneous
OL,13,Ffaults with components on the pole
OL,14,Fsupporting the wire resulted in it
OL,15,Fdropping low enough to make contact
OL,16,Fwith Mr Oates.
OL,18,FFollowing the coroner's findings in
OL,19,FDecember last year, a report to
OL,20,Fprevent future deaths was published.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/11
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,354,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1775207142
OL,3,CFamily of electrocuted runner say not
OL,4,Cenough being done to similar future
OL,5,Cdeaths
OL,7,FThe Energy Network Association (ENA)
OL,8,Fhas since responded to that report.
OL,10,FMalcolm Oates told ITV Border: "We're
OL,11,Ffairly disappointed that it's taken
OL,12,Fthis long for them to start any,
OL,13,Fdiscussions with their members.
OL,15,F"Our interpretation of it, it's almost
OL,16,Fjust like a consultation and advisory
OL,17,Fprocess, that doesn't appear to be
OL,18,Fanything mandatory in that they're
OL,19,Fsaying that their members should do."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/11
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,354,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1775207142
OL,3,CFamily of electrocuted runner say not
OL,4,Cenough being done to similar future
OL,5,Cdeaths
OL,7,FRos Oates said: "At the moment, these
OL,8,Finsulators, as in Harry's case, which
OL,9,Fhave been on the line since 1959.
OL,11,F"It's probably just a matter of time
OL,12,Fbefore it could happen again.
OL,14,F"We just want to prevent it happening
OL,15,Fagain, our own purpose in this is to
OL,16,Fstop this happening to another family.
OL,17,FTo somebody else."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/11
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,354,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1775207142
OL,3,CFamily of electrocuted runner say not
OL,4,Cenough being done to similar future
OL,5,Cdeaths
OL,7,FThe ENA, has published two key
OL,8,Fobjectives, the first being to "Review
OL,9,Fand improve where necessary, Safety,
OL,10,FHealth and Environment (SHE) industry
OL,11,Fstandards and public safety risk
OL,12,Fassessment".
OL,14,FIt will look at improving necessary
OL,15,Fsafety measures, with risk targeted
OL,16,Finspections and patrols.
OL,18,FThe second objective is to "Review and
OL,19,Fimprove engineering evidence, asset
OL,20,Frisk awareness and promote risk-based
OL,21,Finvestment".
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/11
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,354,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1775207142
OL,3,CFamily of electrocuted runner say not
OL,4,Cenough being done to similar future
OL,5,Cdeaths
OL,7,FHis parents welcomed the report and
OL,8,Fthat action is being taken, but wish
OL,9,Fit went further.
OL,11,FHarry's parents were hoping that the
OL,12,FENA would go further by calling for a
OL,13,Fmandatory replacement to a component
OL,14,Fthat failed, and led to Harrys death.
OL,16,FThe court determined that internal air
OL,17,Fgaps in porcelain insulators caused
OL,18,Ftwo units to fail simultaneously.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G6/11
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,354,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1775207142
OL,3,CFamily of electrocuted runner say not
OL,4,Cenough being done to similar future
OL,5,Cdeaths
OL,7,FThis released a high-voltage wire
OL,8,Fwhich became caught on lower equipment
OL,9,Finstead of hitting the ground. As the
OL,10,Fwire never touched the earth, it
OL,11,Fremained live and went undetected for
OL,12,Ftwo days.
OL,14,FHis parents still visit the location
OL,15,Fwhere Harry died and say he will never
OL,16,Fbe forgotten. They hope no other
OL,17,Ffamily will have to do the same.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G7/11
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,354,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1775207142
OL,3,CFamily of electrocuted runner say not
OL,4,Cenough being done to similar future
OL,5,Cdeaths
OL,7,FHis mother, told ITV Border about the
OL,8,Fongoing pain: "It's heartbreaking. You
OL,9,Fmiss him every minute of every day.
OL,10,FLife is very difficult without him and
OL,11,Fit doesn't get any easier either."
OL,13,FReflecting on their relationship, his
OL,14,Ffather, said: "I know it sounds corny,
OL,15,Fbut he was not only a son, but a best
OL,16,Ffriend and irreplaceable."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G8/11
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
