CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1775207142
OL,3,CFamily of electrocuted runner say not
OL,4,Cenough being done to similar future
OL,5,Cdeaths
OL,7,FA spokesperson for Electricity North
OL,8,FWest said: "Our heartfelt sympathies
OL,9,Fremain with Harry Oates' family at
OL,10,Fthis time. This was a tragic incident
OL,11,Fwhich both the coroner and Health and
OL,12,FSafety Executive noted involved a rare
OL,13,Fand complex sequence of events that
OL,14,Fwere unforeseeable.
OL,16,F"Safety is our number one value, and
OL,17,Fwe will continue to work with other
OL,18,Fdistribution network operators and the
OL,19,Findustry trade body, ENA, on learnings
OL,20,Ffrom this immensely sad accident."
OL,26,@pD@LOUxD@AOU|D@bO]
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G9/11
