PN,35310
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1775207142
OL,3,CFamily of electrocuted runner say not
OL,4,Cenough being done to similar future
OL,5,Cdeaths
OL,7,FA spokesperson for Energy Networks
OL,8,FAssociation said: "Our thoughts are
OL,9,Fwith Mr Oates' loved ones following
OL,10,Fthis tragic event. ENA's members are
OL,11,Fcarefully considering the conclusions
OL,12,Fof the report.
OL,14,F"We are working with our members to
OL,15,Fimplement an action plan, embedding
OL,16,Fany necessary changes into our ongoing
OL,17,Fengineering, safety and assurance
OL,18,Fprocesses, with the aim of reducing
OL,19,Fthe risk of such incidents in the
OL,20,Ffuture.
OL,26,@pD@SOU
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G10/11
